  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The registry is an international, multicenter, observational registry of newly diagnosed
      patients with SCLC.

      Data will be entered into an electronic CRF (eCRF) via Internet access. Treatment plan
      remains the responsibility of the patient's physician and data collected in this registry
      will reflect a &quot;real world&quot; approach of the diagnosis and treatment of patients with SCLC.

      Approximately 60 centres in 13 countries will take part in this registry. It is expected that
      about 500 patients will be recruited during a period of 6 to 9 months according to the
      feasibility.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
