    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or Female &gt;/= 18 years

          -  Diagnosis of small cell lung cancer

          -  Patient newly diagnosed with SCLC

          -  Has given written informed consent (if applicable)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Concurrent history of other neoplasm, except curatively treated basal cell skin cancer
             or adequately treated in-situ carcinoma of the cervix.

          -  Patient presenting with recurrence of SCLC.

          -  Patients who has received any chemotherapy for the SCLC.
      </textblock>
